abstract: The examinations come after cracks expanded into a hole on a jetliner last week and forced it to make an emergency landing.
snippet: The examinations come after cracks expanded into a hole on a jetliner last week and forced it to make an emergency landing.
lead_paragraph: Inspections of Boeing jets widened on Wednesday as Asian and European carriers said they would examine some aircraft as a precaution after cracks expanded into a hole on a Southwest Airlines jetliner last week and forced it to make an emergency landing.

headline.main: Other Carriers Follow Southwest and Inspect 737s
